Storage Gateway vs DataSync

Storage Gateway:
Hybrid Cloud Storage Integration: Storage Gateway is designed to integrate on-premises applications with AWS cloud storage. A bridge of connection point between your on-premises environment and AWS storage. Data transfer is not the main thing here. 
Sotrage gateway like a dropbox client, virtual server allows you access cloud.



Secrets Manager (Repository) vs AWS Certificate Manager (Will issue Certificates)
Secrets Manager... enables you to easily rotate, manage, and retrieve database credentials, API keys, and other secrets throughout their lifecycle 

AWS Certificate Manager is a service that lets you easily provision,manage, and deploy public and private Secure Sockets Layer/TransportLayer Security (SSL/TLS) 
certificates for use with AWS services and your internal connected resources.



https://aws.amazon.com/s3/faqs/


